The front line is shown on the set-up maps provided. Players can also use the hex numbers and river references below. Allied units may be set up on or west/southwest of the line. Axis units may be set up east or southeast of the hexes listed below.

**Start at 2-1701** and follow the Moselle River south to 1-3336 to 3237 to 3238 to 3138 to 2937 to 2639 to 2641 to 2541 to 2548 to 2649 to 2549 to 2550 to 2651 to 2652, to 2752 to 2852 to 2952 to;
**Map-4** Hex 3001 to 2903 to 2905 to 3006 to 3105 to 3107 to 3509 to 3609 to 3810 to 3811 to 3911 to 4011 to 4212 to 4213 to 4313 to 4512 to 4713 to 4715 to;
**Map-3** Hex 1619 to1620 to 1821 to 1822 to 2023 to 2024 to 2124 to 2129 to 2230 to 2231 to 2633 to 2634 to 2734 to 2735 to 2836 to 3137.

**Important:** *The portion of the out of play area, denoted by the red dotted line on map 3 (Nov scenario map) is still active. It is out of play when Interval Four is closed (**LF** (27.1.1)).*
